[B][I]Venticus 639 has been started Officialy Our Project is Based on a 639 Economey Server , Our server provides allot of Minigames , Examples Soulwars, Clan wars, Castle wars , Duel arena , Barrowz And allot more! , Our server provides a Really good Pking system with makes Pking fun and Real , Bossing , Ice barrage has the Same Damage as in R$ , Ancients/Lunars/Modern Are all working Spells , Curses is working now leeching leeches what it needs to / turmoil gives bonus / Soulsplit smites , Our server has allot more Great Features And We Keep adding Allot more to Make everyone happy , Everything of Skilling works , Fletching Arrows\Bows\Bow String , Herblore Making pots All working , Crafting , Making amulets , Bracelets And allot more! , Smithing , Making Armour(s) , Wep(s) ,And allot more everything works! All skills are added and fixed as need to be 100% Working , Range guild Works same as in R$ , Working Teleports, And Allot more Features Check it out! Soon [/B]

[B]VENTICUS STAFF TEAM[/B] Our staff team will help you with anything you need , such as Help how to make money Our staff team Is Active for atleast 9 Hours a day And some are Allot more active then others It depends on the TMZ(S)

[B]Moderators[/B] are People that Look around if Everything goes fine No Spammers , Advers , Flamers , Helping you with Some other things such as stuck, Bugged , Nulled Accounts

[B]Helpers[/B] Are Helping everyone With what they need to be helped with , no Discussions will be done about anything , Questions will be Answered so fast as possible Its their Job to do
